						<summary>

						<p>Piṅgaḷa = c. 16th Century.</p>						

						<p>This records a deed of asylum given by Kōṉērirāya-pallavarāyar and others of Peruṅgōḻiyūr to the temple of Tirukkuṉṟākkuḍi-uḍaiya-nāyiṉār temple and the nāḍu of Iraṇḍumalai-nāḍu seeking protection for their lives and property.</p>						

