<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrīma</hi>ṉ piṅkalavaru<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>m Āṉi mātam <hi rend="grantha"><num value="25">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 5</num> nāḷ</hi> kāṭṭunāṭu Āṉa
<lb n="2"/>ceyaciṅkakulakāla vaḷanāṭṭu vaṭapaṉaṅkāṭṭu nāṭṭu Uṭaiyār
<lb n="3"/>tirukkuṉṟākkuṭi Uṭaiya nayiṉāṟkkum Iraṇṭumalai nāṭṭukkum
<lb n="4"/>peruṅkōḷiūr Aracavveṉiyamāvala Iṭaperumāṉ
<lb n="5"/>kōṉēri Irācapallavarāyar Uḷḷiṭṭārōm Ā<hi rend="grantha">śri</hi>ya
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kal veṭṭiṉa namakku Uṇṭu Āṉa viṉaippāṭṭu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>kkum Attakāṉi pirāṇakāṉi maṟṟum Eṟpayiṟpaṭṭa
<lb n="8"/><hi rend="grantha">jī</hi>vataṉam pakaiyaṅkaḷukkum Aḻivu cōṟuvupaṭṭu cakiyittum
<lb n="9"/>nōkkak kaṭavarkaḷ Ākavum §
</p>

